title: 242: Ranking the Heisman finalists as NFL prospects
itunes:title: 242: Ranking the Heisman finalists as NFL prospects
description:
Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis preview the biggest week 14 games by picking the players you have to watch this weekend (8:37). Rhett and Bucky also react to the Browns firing GM Sashi Brown (4:46). The guys wrap the show by projecting which Heisman Trophy finalists will be the most successful pro (40:42).
